{"type":"message","id":"dc13d97f","parentId":"f7842fdf","timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:05:45.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The report confirms the task failed. The system tried to analyze logs but hit an EISDIR error. This is a code bug in the smart-explore.js script.\n\nSince this is a cron job that's meant to run autonomously, and it's a scheduled task (not a direct user request), I should:\n\n1. Check if there's a HEARTBEAT.md or similar instruction file\n2. See if I should fix the bug or just report it\n3. Not spam the user with messages about failed cron jobs\n\nLet me check if there are any instructions about handling cron job failures.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"The autonomous exploration cron job encountered a bug - it tried to read a directory as a file (EISDIR error) when analyzing logs. This is a code issue in the `smart-explore.js` script that needs fixing.\n\nSince this is an automated scheduled task, I'll document this for later attention rather than waking you up at 4 AM. The issue is in the log analysis code - it needs to properly handle directories and read individual files within them."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_88afaf13c95b40d2b02f7bd3","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-12.md","content":"# 2026-03-12 每日记录\n\n## 04:05 - 自主探索系统错误\n\n**Cron 任务失败**: `autonomous-exploration` (04:00 AM)\n\n- **任务**: 分析日志文件，发现错误模式和优化机会\n- **错误**: `EISDIR: illegal operation on a directory, read`\n- **原因**: `executor/smart-explore.js` 尝试将目录作为文件读取\n- **位置**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/autonomous-exploration/executor/smart-explore.js`\n\n**待修复**: \n- 日志分析功能需要遍历目录中的文件，而不是直接读取目录\n- 代码应该使用 `fs.readdir()` 获取文件列表，然后逐个读取\n\n**影响**: \n- 29 个 cron 任务中，这个自主探索任务失败\n- 不影响其他系统功能\n- 需要在合适时间修复代码\n\n**相关文件**:\n- 报告: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/autonomous-exploration/reports/exploration-1773259519686.json`\n- 脚本: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/autonomous-exploration/executor/smart-explore.js`\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":497,"output":509,"cacheRead":10560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11566,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773259529902}}
